d games are challenging enough to keep you progressing and simple enough to enjoy every day — at any age or skill level.\n\nDISCOVER YOUR COGNITIVE PROFILE\nGo deeper with a library of self-discovery tests that reveal how your mind truly works:\n- IQ tests & Cognitive strengths\n- Personality type and archetype insights\n- Emotional intelligence and self-awareness tests\nEach test comes with personalized recommendations so you know exactly which areas to focus on and how to grow.\n\nTRACK YOUR GROWTH\n- See your performance trends over time\n- Get actionable insights — not just scores\n- Stay motivated with streaks and progress reports\n\nWHY IMPULSE\nMost brain apps just give you games. Impulse also gives you deeper understanding of yourself. \nTrain smarter and stay sharp for life.\nJoin 100 million people worldwide who've made Impulse part of their daily routine.\n\nImpulse offers a 3-day free trial with full access to all games - no ads, no interruptions. If you choose to subscribe, the fee will be shown in the app before you complete the payment. Payment will be charged to your iTunes Account at confirmation of purchase. Subscription automatically renews unless auto-renewal is turned off at least 24 hours before the end of the current period. You may manage your subscription and turn off auto-renewal at any time in your iTunes Account Settings.\n\nTerms of Service: https://brainimpulse.me/app/tos.html\nPrivacy Policy: https://brainimpulse.me/app/privacy_policy.html\nContact: support@brainimpulse.me","minimumOsVersion":"16.0","trackId":1451295827,"trackName":"Impulse - Brain Training Games","genres":["Health & Fitness","Education"],"userRatingCount":3809}